<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBi9_00091" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBi9_00091_F001">
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">６―さくら<sampling type="start" />の家・表</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　江戸川の堤の側にあるさくらの家。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　朝日を浴びて自転車に乗った高校生たちが行く。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　博と満男の親子が、土手をジョギング姿で下りてくる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　家の前に辿り着き、荒い息を吐きながらしゃがみこむ満男。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">博</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「体が鈍ってるんだよ。</sentence>
<sentence>基礎体力がないんじゃないか、お前。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">基礎学力もだけど」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　玄関を入る博。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うるさいなあ、朝からぶつぶつ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　後に続く満男。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">７―同・居間</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　朝食の支度をしているさくら。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　博と満男が入ってくる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">博</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「明日から毎日つきあえ、徹底的に鍛えなおしてやるから」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どうしたの？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">博</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「帝釈天まで行ったら息切れしてさ、タクシーで帰ろうなんて言いやがるんだ、あのバカ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「駄目ねえ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　満男、ドタドタと二階に上がっていく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　牛乳をうまそうに飲み干す博。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">８―同・二階・満男の部屋</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　寝起きのままの散らかった室内。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　入ってきた満男、シャツを脱ぎ捨て、乱暴に鞄を取ってノートを詰める。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　机の上に置いてあった定期入れが床に落ちる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　拾い上げる満男、ふと中に挟んである写真を見つめる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　セーラー服を着た満男のガールフレンド、及川泉が微笑んでいる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">９―同・居間</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　コーヒーを入れる博。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　トーストにバターを塗るさくら。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　鞄を持った満男が、階段を下りてきて椅子に座るとコーヒーカップを差し出す。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　不機嫌な顔でコーヒーを注ぐ博。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ありがとうございます」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　博、変な顔をする。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「母さん、明日火曜日だろう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そうだったかしら」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「泉ちゃんの店、休みなんだ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ねえ、今夜連れてきていいかな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　さくら、苦笑しながら答える。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">「いいわよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「この間電話したらさ、寮の食事はあまりおいしくないなんて言ってたし」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">博</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「もう何カ月になるんだ、東京へ出てきて？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　満男、愛想よく答える。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「四月からだから、四、五、六、七、八―そろそろ半年だよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「何が好きだったんだっけ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「グラタン。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">いつかうまいうまいって食べてたじゃないか」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「わかった。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">じゃ、作っておくからね」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「お願いします。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">―じゃ、父さん、行ってきます」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　鞄を取り上げ、いそいそと玄関に向かう。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「帰りは？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">満男</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「俺、店に迎えに行くけど、七時ぐらいになるんじゃないかな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">じゃ、行ってきます」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　勢いよく表に出て行く満男。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">１０―同・表</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　満男、スキップを踏みながら土手道を上がっていく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">１１―同・居間</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　さくら、椅子に腰を下ろす。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">博</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「何だ、泉ちゃんが来る時だけ愛想ふりまきやがって」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「でも、家に連れてくるだけましじゃない。</sentence>
<sentence>普通は外で二人きりで会いたがるものよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">若い子同士は」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">博</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「金がないんだろう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">さくら</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「それもあるかもしれないけど、ほら、泉ちゃんは母子家庭でしょう、お母さんは家で料理作るような人じゃないらしいし。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">だから家庭の味を味わわせてやりたいって気持があるのよ、満男には」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　博、読<sampling type="end" />んでいた新聞を机の上に置く。</sentence>
</paragraph>
</article>
</sample>
